snippet.title: Dastan TV
snippet.description:
Hi Friends.
This is your friend Dastan.
Welcome to my Youtube Channel.

This channel uploads daily content related with Hollywood, Bollywood and Tv Series both Hindi and English.
Also giving Cast and Crew information.
I also give daily updates related with DC extended universe and dc comics

Recently i have started to review movies and tv serials.
The Main Audience Targeted by the channel  is from Indian Subcontinent.

The Channel sole purpose is to provide entertainment and not to hurt anyone's emotions or beliefs.
If anyone has any issue with any one of my content , you are free to ask me to take it down.
Love Respect and Unity To all
take Care
